Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=Solar Symbolism
By: St Gregory of Nyssa
---
Travelling through the creation, the virtuous man is led to the
apprehension of a Master of the creation; ... when he observes the
beauty of this material sunlight, he grasps by analogy the beauty of
the real sunlight.
